      "description": "<p>Experience timeless elegance with our Chanderi Embroidered Kurta Set, featuring a beautifully crafted Kurta, matching Pants, and a delicate Dupatta. Made from premium Chanderi fabric, this set showcases intricate embroidery, offering a luxurious feel and graceful drape. Perfect for festive occasions, celebrations, and special gatherings, this ensemble blends tradition with sophistication.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>100% Original Products</p>\n<p>Pay-on Delivery Might Be Available</p>\n<p>Easy 7-Day Returns and Exchanges</p>\n<p><strong>Product Details </strong></p>\n<p>Elegant Chanderi Embroidered Kurta with Trousers and Dupatta</p>\n<p><strong>Kurta design:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gold Polka Printed</li>\n<li>Straight Fit</li>\n<li>3/4 Sleeves</li>\n<li>Calf length with Straight hem</li>\n<li>Viscose Chanderi Silk Machine Weave Fabric</li>\n<li>100% Cotton Lining</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Trousers design:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Solid Trousers</li>\n<li>Partially Elasticated Waistband</li>\n<li>Slip-On Closure</li>\n<li>Pocket 2</li>\n<li>Viscose PST Machine Weave Fabric</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Dupatta Design:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Elegant Solid Dupatta with Gota Border</li>\n<li>Machine Weave Net Fabric</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Material:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Top Fabric: Viscose Chanderi Slik</li>\n<li>Lining Fabric: 100% Cotton</li>\n<li>Bottom Fabric: Viscose PST</li>\n<li>Dupatta Fabric: Net</li>\n</ul>\n",
